column11:
  Let $p$ be a prime and let $x$ be a $p$-adic integer. We provide two
supercongruences for truncated series of the form $$\sum_{k=1}^{p-1}
\frac{(x)_k}{(1)_k}\cdot \frac{1}{k}\sum_{1\le j_1\le\cdots\le j_r\le
k}\frac{1}{j_1^{}\cdots j_r^{}}\quad\mbox{and}\quad \sum_{k=1}^{p-1}
\frac{(x)_k(1-x)_k}{(1)_k^2}\cdot \frac{1}{k}\sum_{1\le j_1\le\cdots\le j_r\le
k}\frac{1}{j_1^{2}\cdots j_r^{2}}.$$
